net.dragondelve.customdriversutil.model

Class Track

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dragondelve.customdriversutil.model.Track

  • public final class Track
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an in game track. Stores all properties to allow an automatic generation of track specific overrides. This class is fully annotated with JAXB for easy XML conversion.
